definition: variant of 百葉窗|百叶窗[bai3 ye4 chuang1]

sentences.english: The series can be accompanied by one hundred sash.
sentences.chinese: 該系列產品均可配上百頁窗扇。

sentences.english: New renovation, wooden blind, sell or rent with partial furniture, direct owner, no commission.
sentences.chinese: 新裝修連部份家俬，木百頁窗簾，業主自讓免傭。

sentences.english: Tore open the shutters and threw up the sash.
Motorised adjustable louvres in the external walls control the amount of air supplied to the underfloor space.
sentences.chinese: 在外牆上機動化的百頁窗控制地板內的空氣流量。
